  <brief_title>A Phase 3 Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of HCP1303 Capsules</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Phase 3 Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of HCP1303 Capsules</official_title>
