  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of this study is to evaluate efficacy and safety of HCP1301 capsule in
      patients with Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia and Erectile Dysfunction
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A multicenter, randomized, double-blind, phase 3 clinical trial to evaluate the efficacy and
      safety of HCP1303 capsule
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
